Photo Plastic Surgery Pro is a very professional, powerful and easy-to-use application that allows you to edit digital photos to simulate the results of orthopedics and to beautify your photos to achieve the desired results. The main functions are as follows:

1. Facial shaping:
(1) Face shaping: under the bar, cheeks, face width;
(2) Eye shaping: eye size, position, angle, distance;
(3) Eyebrow shaping: eyebrow size, position, angle, distance;
(4) Nose shaping: nose width, height, size, position, nose tip;
(5) Mouth shaping: mouth width, height, size, position;

2. Facial beauty:
(1) Microdermabrasion: smoothing the facial skin;
(2) Whitening: whitening the facial skin;

3.Acne:
Use this tool to quickly achieve skin texture, so as to achieve a lot of treatment effects, such as: remove scars, eliminate acne, eliminate facial stains, eye bags and so on.

4.Free deformation:
This tool can be used to easily stretch, scale, rotate to achieve a lot of shaping effects, such as breast augmentation, thin waist, stovepipe, thin abdomen, strong muscles, etc. In addition, use free deformation tools Used for face deformation can produce a lot of funny effects.

Disclaimer: Although we have tried to simulate the results of cosmetic surgery as much as possible, there may be a huge difference between actual and simulated results. The software is just a digital image processing application that gives you a reference through simulation results and cannot be used as a basis for your final decision. We do not accept any responsibility in this regard. Only certified surgeons can assess the achievable goals. You must always evaluate with a qualified surgeon before considering any cosmetic surgery procedures.
